  "texts": [
    "The three-point 'Red', 'Amber', and 'Green' scores have the following associated recommendations for action primarily of relevance to government actors:",
    "Composite score and explanation of recommended actions.",
    "For tools scoring 'Red', a targeted follow-up assessment is recommended to better understand their misuse potential.",
    "This could include:",
    "• Deeper technical evaluations • Red teaming exercises • Integration into existing threat models."
  ]
}